title: Citizen Eco-Drive AT 2.0 Mens Watch AW115007E Overview
description:
Citizen Eco-Drive AR 2.0 Stainless Steel And Black Mens Watch - AW1150-07E - http://www.abt.com/product/65292/Citizen-AW115007E.html

Take action and show your inner drive with the rich and sporty styling of AR 2.0. Proprietary black chroma finishing enhances the 44.5mm stainless steel case while the dial sports a modern black pinstripe design. Features include date luminous hands and 100M WR. The crown’s distinctive “D” and the straps pierced leather design complete this edgy look. From the Citizen Design Studios Drive from Citizen Eco-Drive is fueled by light any light so it never needs a battery.
Specifications:
• Movement: Eco-Drive J810
• Functions: 3-Hand with Date
• Band: Black Polyurethane Band Buckle
• Case Size: 44mm
• Case Material: Two Tone Stainless Steel
• Dial: Metal Dial
• Crystal: Mineral Crystal
• Water-Resistance: WR100 - 333ft (100m)
